                            Charon (Part 3: Asphodel)
                        </div>
                    

                    

                    



                    <div id="page-content">
                        

<div style="text-align: center;">
<blockquote>
<p>&#171; <a href="/charon-part-2-katabasis">Charon (Part 2: Katabasis)</a> || Charon (Part 3: Asphodel) || ??? &#187;<br />
&#171;&#171; <a href="/charon-part-1-nekyia">Charon (Part 1: Nekyia)</a></p>
</blockquote>
